subject: NCAA Basketball Championships (Women)
Basketball (College)
lead_paragraph: Alyssa Thomas scored a career-high 33 points and grabbed 13 rebounds as fourth-seeded Maryland upset the No. 1 seed Tennessee, 73-62, on Sunday.
